title: Surviving Mars SPACE RACE-CODEX
description:
Note: Initial seeding will be done for 48 hours

C O D E X
P R E S E N T S

Surviving Mars: Space Race (c) Paradox Interactive
Release Date: 11/2018 Protection: Steam
Discs: 1 Genre: Simulation

Compete for milestones and anomalies with several other AI colonies
backed by rival sponsors attempting to become this planets
superpower. You can trade with, respond to distress calls for
issue distress calls to, and even steal important colonists from
these competitor colonies as you establish your territory on
Mars.NARRATIVE EVENTS Experience narrative events throughout your
colonization process that help reveal the realities of life in the
dome and challenge your management skills
